1. Doctor

    Story: As a Doctor, I want to view a patient's medical history, so that I can provide accurate diagnoses and treatments.
        Acceptance Criteria:
            System displays past diagnoses, medications, and allergies.
            Doctor can filter history by date or record type.
        Priority: High
        Story Points: 5
    Story: As a Doctor, I want to manage my daily appointment schedule, so that I can optimize my workflow and reduce patient wait times.
        Acceptance Criteria:
            Calendar view updates in real-time as patients book or cancel.
            Doctor can mark appointments as "complete" or "no-show."
        Priority: Medium
        Story Points: 3

2. Patient

    Story: As a Patient, I want to book an appointment online, so that I can schedule my visit conveniently without calling the clinic.
        Acceptance Criteria:
            Patient can view available time slots for specific doctors.
            A confirmation email is sent immediately after booking.
        Priority: High
        Story Points: 8
    Story: As a Patient, I want to receive automated appointment reminders, so that I can ensure I don't miss my scheduled consultations.
        Acceptance Criteria:
            SMS/Email reminders are sent 24 hours prior to the appointment.
            Reminders include a "cancel/reschedule" link.
        Priority: Medium
        Story Points: 3

3. Admin

    Story: As an Admin, I want to manage user accounts and permissions, so that I can ensure only authorized personnel access sensitive medical data.
        Acceptance Criteria:
            Admin can assign roles (Doctor, Patient, Staff) to new accounts.
            Admin can deactivate accounts for former employees.
        Priority: High
        Story Points: 5
    Story: As an Admin, I want to generate monthly clinic performance reports, so that I can analyze patient volume and improve resource allocation.
        Acceptance Criteria:
            System generates a PDF showing total appointments and cancellations per month.
            Reports show average patient wait times per doctor.
        Priority: Low
        Story Points: 5
